Getting Started for Instructors

<p>Welcome to <%= SITE_NAME %>! This page provides a general introduction to OpenStax Tutor and describes what is required to set up your class. </p>
  
<p>We recommend you begin by watching our introductory screencasts. Next, check out our roadmap of the steps involved in setting up your class in <%= SITE_NAME %>. The overview explains the general process without going into too much detail. If you'd like to learn more about any particular step, click on the links in the roadmap. </p>

Screencasts -- 5 minute introduction to OST, adding course content, creating assignments, setting up learning and feedback conditions
 
